thread.title: Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3

title: Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3
text:
> Sports Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3 Kansas City Royals first baseman Eric Hosmer gets hit in the face with a foul ball during the fifth inning in Game 3 of baseball's American League Championship Series against the Toronto Blue Jays on Monday, Oct. 19, 2015, in Toronto. (AP Photo/Charlie Riedel)
